0x0B4DF1FA60C0E664.name: SHOW_HUD_COMPONENT_THIS_FRAME
0x0B4DF1FA60C0E664.comment:
This function hides various HUD (Heads-up Display) components.
Listed below are the integers and the corresponding HUD component.
- 1 : WANTED_STARS
- 2 : WEAPON_ICON
- 3 : CASH
- 4 : MP_CASH
- 5 : MP_MESSAGE
- 6 : VEHICLE_NAME
- 7 : AREA_NAME
- 8 : VEHICLE_CLASS
- 9 : STREET_NAME
- 10 : HELP_TEXT
- 11 : FLOATING_HELP_TEXT_1
- 12 : FLOATING_HELP_TEXT_2
- 13 : CASH_CHANGE
- 14 : RETICLE
- 15 : SUBTITLE_TEXT
- 16 : RADIO_STATIONS
- 17 : SAVING_GAME
- 18 : GAME_STREAM
- 19 : WEAPON_WHEEL
- 20 : WEAPON_WHEEL_STATS
- 21 : HUD_COMPONENTS
- 22 : HUD_WEAPONS

These integers also work for the `HIDE_HUD_COMPONENT_THIS_FRAME` native, but instead hides the HUD Component.
